name: AAAaaavacado
description:
A great loss

It's very scary to lose yourself. Especially if it is a consequence of the influence of other people, or a person. Although circumstances can also play a large role in the loss of one's original self. It is really frightening when a person gives up his own ideals, priorities, everything that is sacred to himself, in favor of his instincts. Because the external is always just a pretext to justify inner desires.
